<br>
My only suggestion would be to schedule a raid like this for a weekend, since things like the MA and MHeal having to get up for work in the morning can seriously put a crimp in everyone's plans.  I understand that this was essentially a &quot;cash farming&quot; raid to help fund Sky, but seeing a few named up close would have been nice.<br>
<br>
Seeing the monk DT'd by Fright was a close second though.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
